FBIS4-68188 "jptot021__l94054" JPRS-TOT-94-021-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 18 May 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Arrest Evidence Indicates Greece Training PKK Arrest Evidence Indicates Greece Training PKK Defense Minister's Statement NC1805152294 Athens ELEVTHEROTIPIA in Greek 18 May 94 p 4 NC1805152294 Athens ELEVTHEROTIPIA Greek BFN [Excerpt] Istanbul--[passage omitted] Turkish National Defense Minister Mehmet Golhan noted: "Germany and France have banned the activities of this organization." The Turkish minister added: "We expect similar behavior from other countries. However, this is not done by certain neighbors, such as Greece. We have learned, through confessions by members of this organization, that certain people are trained in that country."
